  "lyrics": "What? What's that in the sky? Oh my god, is that a fuckin' alien? Are you takin' me high? On your world magical ride? Are you takin' me high, alien? Gotta visit that station, maybe it's alien Have your light beam comin' from above Take me to another place, take me to another one Take me to another high, take me to the sky You're alien, you're alien Station in new ruins, seeping into my life You're alien, baby, you're alien Watching your station seep inside of my eyes Pull me up, pull me up in your sleep, baby Pull me up, pull me up in your dreams Alien space and time Like creators in the one we all space, yeah And I can fly Na na na, you wanna come and be a part of me You're just power here, come and just talk to me There's no doubt we're here I'm not competing I'm not for your show You're alien, you're alien In your station, you're alien, alien My alien, it's just alien to me It's just alien to me And this dichotomy of light and power And your wrong desires to devour this I'm just an alien in mind Just an alien in mind So alien in mind Remind me, driving alien Nothing to show here, nothing to see Go away, go away Yeah, nothing to see here Just go away Don't cross this line, baby, it's alien The thought of you without me",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 14.880000114440918,
      "text": "What? What's that in the sky? Oh my god, is that a fuckin' alien?",
      "start": 7.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 25.1200008392334,
      "text": "Are you takin' me high? On your world magical ride?",
      "start": 14.880000114440918
    },
    {
      "end": 31.420000076293945,
      "text": "Are you takin' me high, alien?",
      "start": 27.780000686645508
    },
    {
      "end": 40.41999816894531,
      "text": "Gotta visit that station, maybe it's alien",
      "start": 35.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 48.79999923706055,
      "text": "Have your light beam comin' from above",
      "start": 43.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 55.7400016784668,
      "text": "Take me to another place, take me to another one",
      "start": 48.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 65.13999938964844,
      "text": "Take me to another high, take me to the sky",
      "start": 56.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 72.68000030517578,
      "text": "You're alien, you're alien",
      "start": 65.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 81.19999694824219,
      "text": "Station in new ruins, seeping into my life",
      "start": 74.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 88.62000274658203,
      "text": "You're alien, baby, you're alien",
      "start": 81.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 98.08000183105469,
      "text": "Watching your station seep inside of my eyes",
      "start": 90.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 107.0999984741211,
      "text": "Pull me up, pull me up in your sleep, baby",
      "start": 98.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 114.26000213623047,
      "text": "Pull me up, pull me up in your dreams",
      "start": 107.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 120.94000244140625,
      "text": "Alien space and time",
      "start": 117.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 126.36000061035156,
      "text": "Like creators in the one we all space, yeah",
      "start": 120.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 129.8000030517578,
      "text": "And I can fly",
      "start": 126.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 134.77999877929688,
      "text": "Na na na, you wanna come and be a part of me",
      "start": 130.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 138.67999267578125,
      "text": "You're just power here, come and just talk to me",
      "start": 134.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 140.82000732421875,
      "text": "There's no doubt we're here",
      "start": 138.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 143.5,
      "text": "I'm not competing",
      "start": 140.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 147.82000732421875,
      "text": "I'm not for your show",
      "start": 144.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 155.1999969482422,
      "text": "You're alien, you're alien",
      "start": 148.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 164,
      "text": "In your station, you're alien, alien",
      "start": 157.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 169.3800048828125,
      "text": "My alien, it's just alien to me",
      "start": 165
    },
    {
      "end": 171.5,
      "text": "It's just alien to me",
      "start": 169.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 176.63999938964844,
      "text": "And this dichotomy of light and power",
      "start": 171.5
    },
    {
      "end": 182.1199951171875,
      "text": "And your wrong desires to devour this",
      "start": 176.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 183.82000732421875,
      "text": "I'm just an alien in mind",
      "start": 182.1199951171875
    },
    {
